dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Minneapolis, Minnesota, last revised 1930, Volume 8
dct_description_sm: Updated with pasteover slips and additional sheets. Date of last revision varies between 1924-1930. Each volume includes a map of ward lines and district lines and a volume boundary map (index map to all volumes).
